latestIgtvVideos.title: In Vogue
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here is the woman glowing in traditional pink lehenga like a goddess. The skin is radiant and the attitude is reflecting the confidence.

For such self glowing lady the makeup is kept simple and neutral. The base is skin toned, the blush is natural pink, the tips are highlighted and the lips are defined with pink.

The minimal make up in pink attire is the perfect choice for women or brides who want to keep it simple yet elegant and classy.
